<h1>WhatPulse Data</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <h3>Client API</h3>
            <div class="col s12 m6">
                <div class="card green darken-1">
                    <div class="card-content white-text">
                    <span class="card-title">Executing a Pulse</span>
                    <p>http://localhost:3490/v1/unpulsed</p>
                    <p>You can remotely execute a pulse via the Client API.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6">
                <div class="card green darken-1">
                    <div class="card-content white-text">
                    <span class="card-title">Unpulsed Stats</span>
                    <p>http://localhost:3490/v1/unpulsed</p>
                    <p>The stats that are accumulated between pulses is accessible through this call. Get the unpulsed clicks, keys, download (in bytes), upload (in bytes) and uptime (in seconds).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <h3>Web API</h3>
            <div class="col s12 m6">
                <div class="card light-blue darken-1">
                    <div class="card-content white-text">
                    <span class="card-title">Pulse Stats</span>
                    <p>/pulses.php?user= userid or username</p>
                    <p>This API endpoint allows you to get a list of pulses for a user.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-action">
                    <a href="http://api.whatpulse.org/pulses.php?user={{name}}">See Data</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col s12 m6">
                <div class="card light-blue darken-1">
                    <div class="card-content white-text">
                    <span class="card-title">User Stats</span>
                    <p>/user.php?user= userid or username</p>
                    <p>With this call, you can retrieve all the stats from a user based on a username or user ID.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-action">
                    <a href="http://api.whatpulse.org/user.php?user={{name}}">See Data</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m6">
                <div class="card light-blue darken-1">
                    <div class="card-content white-text">
                    <span class="card-title">Team Stats</span>
                    <p>/team.php?team= userid or username</p>
                    <p>This API endpoint gets you all statistics of a certain team.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>